HEADWORD: Anno Domini
<hw>An"no Dom"i*ni</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[L., in the year of
[our] Lord [Jesus Christ]; usually abbrev. <sc>a. d.</sc>]</ety> <def>In
the year of the Christian era; as, <sc>a. d.</sc> 1887.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

